                            </p>
                            <p>
                                <strong>Minimum:</strong> Dual Core CPU, 4 GB RAM, CentOS 7.8, FileMaker Server 19 or newer
                            </p>
                            <a href="{$basePath}/download/24uToolboxPlugIn321Linux.zip" target="_blank" class="button ga-track-download-file">Download</a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="gr-3 gr-12@tablet gr-12@mobile">
                            <h3>iOS</h3>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    macOS 11.3 or newer
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    FileMaker Pro 19.6 or newer (for creating FileMaker solutions)
